TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
what? KILL IT WITH MORE FIRE!

waiter there's soup in soup in soup in pie in soup in my hamburger. WHY IS SOUP IN MY HAMBUGER

its our new special, can you read?

Waiter, theres a super suit in my suit!

Sorry we are specialists in soup not suits.

Waiter my soup is waiting for the waiter, which waiting for someone waiting.

Indeed.

Waiter, there are feathers in my soup, a flaming one, an ice covered one, and a steel electric one.

Sorry, but we ran out of chicken. But we had some Phoenix, snow owl and cyborg turkey left.

Waiter, why is there a Staff Assisant in my soup?

To assist the staff, why else?

Waiter, there's SOUP in my soup bowl!

So sorry for the inconvenience.

*drains soup from soup bowl*

Waiter, there's a live chicken in my soup!

I'm sorry, we thought all of them were fully gassed...

Waiter, there's some intergranular corrosion in my soup!

Eat it quickly, before it totally decays then.

WAITER! There is a live lawyer in my soup!

I hope you have a better one, he doesn't look happy.

Waiter, there's a miniature canoe in my soup!

You want a bigger one?

Waiter, why is my soup in bread? (sorry, wanted to change my answers up a bit)

Because you've poured it there.

Waiter, why there is plane debris in my soup?

`

Edited February 7, 2021 by LVL 9001

It makes the flaver more explosive.

Waiter, theres a waiter in my soup!

That's the spoon.

Waiter, there are beans in my soup!

Sir, those aren't beans. That's not even a bowl of soup. I suggest you get out of the dumpster and go into the restaurant.

Waiter, there's a finger in my soup!

See, if you do this trick with the fingers up close to the eyes, you can make them look like sausages!

Waiter, there's a virtual reality headset in my soup!

Wear it, then the soup can be a lie.

Waiter! There are Stack Overflows in my soup!

Oh, sorry, I will bring you some more stack holders and salt.

Waiter, there is a fissile disciplinary loaf in my soup!

? No idea what that is... But just to be safe, don't eat it and run away from it.

Waiter, there is a blown-up Falcon 9 first stage in my soup!

Well, you did order the Atlantic soup!

Waiter, there's a LEM in my soup!

Um, what's that?

Waiter, theres a fissle sheld in my soup!

Oh, sorry. I'll bring you a Missile Shed instead. Also, that rhymed.

Waiter, there's a spoon in my soup!

oh sorry sir. here have a fork instead.

Waiter, Danny2462 is in my soup!

Don't touch it or the whole universe will glit-

Waiter! There are divisions by 0 in my soup !
